<!--index.wxml-->
<view class="container">
  <view class="myVideoSection">
    <video 
      id="myVideo" 
      src="https://shengshiyunyou.oss-cn-guangzhou.aliyuncs.com/template/exp_01001.mp4" 
      binderror="videoErrorCallback" 
      show-center-play-btn='{{true}}' 
      show-play-btn="{{true}}" 
      controls
      poster="https://ss0.bdstatic.com/70cFuHSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy/it/u=3871678567,2844469471&fm=26&gp=0.jpg"
      object-fit="cover"
      picture-in-picture-mode="{{['push', 'pop']}}"
      style="width:100%;height:240px"
    ></video>    
  </view>  
  <view class="mainbox headerbox">
    <h3>珠海横琴长隆海洋王国珠海横琴长隆海洋王国珠海横琴长aaa隆海洋王国aaa</h3>
    <p>珠海长隆海洋王国</p>
    <p>时长：45秒</p>
    <p>需上传视频：3段</p>
    <h5>￥431.21</h5>
    <button class=" btn shareBtn" open-type="share" bindtap="onShareAppMessage"> <image src="../../images/share.png"></image>分享</button>
  </view>   
  <view class="mainbox">
    <view class="addBVideo">
      <p>请根据视频提示，在下方分别拍摄或上传视频，我们将快速为您剪辑生成视频，大师手笔，一触即达</p>
      <ul class="addList">
        <li wx:for="{{arrayList}}" wx:key="id">
          <view class="addSelect" wx:if="{{item.img==''}}" bindtap="selectVideo" data-index="{{index}}">
            <image src="{{item.imgUrl}}" class="addimg"></image>
            上传视频
          </view>
          <view class="selectedImg" wx:else>
            <image src="{{item.img}}" class="imgSize"></image>
            <text>{{item.duration}}</text>
            <button class="deleVideo" bindtap="deleVideoBtn" data-index="{{index}}"><image src="../../images/ashbin.png"></image></button>
          </view>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </view>    
    <view class="submitBox">
      <label class="radio">
        <radio value="r1" checked="true"/>我已阅读并同意<a>《视频制作协议》</a>
      </label>
      <button class="btn" bindtap="goToMakeVideo">开始制作</button>
  </view>
</view>  
</view>
